comment: I found my dream home through this website! The search filters were very helpful.
Great selection of properties. I wish the photos were more high-resolution though.
Some listings were outdated and already sold. It would be helpful to have more accurate information.
Smooth process from browsing to closing the deal. Excellent support from the customer service team!
The website layout is confusing, and the search function needs improvement. Had trouble finding what I was looking for.
Found some great options within my budget. The map feature helped me narrow down my choices effectively.
I appreciate the detailed descriptions provided for each property. Made it easier to compare and decide.
It would be nice to have more options for virtual tours. Many listings lacked this feature.
The property alerts feature is very useful. I was notified immediately when a new listing matching my criteria became available.
Overall satisfied with the website's user experience. Found my new home within a week of searching!
